high_descs: Turn to the right and then left to face the bed.
Pick the book on the left up from the bed.
Turn around and cross the room to stand at the end of the desk near the trash can.
Put the book on the desk.
anns.task_desc: Put a book on a desk.

high_descs: Look down, turn right, walk to the night stand beside the bed, then make a quick left to face the bed.
Grab the book in front of the laptop on the bed.
Turn around and walk to the desk to your right.
Place the book on the desk.
anns.task_desc: Place the book in front of the laptop on the bed on the desk.

high_descs: Turn right, walk forward a step, then turn left to face the bed
Pick up the left-most magazine off of the bed
Turn around, walk forward till you hit a wall, then turn right.
Place the magazine on the desk.
anns.task_desc: Move a magazine from the bed to the desk.
